com.fluidops.ajax.components

Class FAbstractTextInputWithAutosuggestion<D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fluidops.ajax.components.FComponent
      • com.fluidops.ajax.components.FContainer
        • com.fluidops.ajax.components.FAbstractTextInputWithAutosuggestion<D>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FTextInput2

    public abstract class FAbstractTextInputWithAutosuggestion<D>
extends FContainer
    Abstract class for a generic autocompletion text input box (contains most of the content previously in FTextInput2). If no suggestions are available, is a normal input field.
    Author:
    uli, as
